bby.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHand-glazed terracotta frieze by \u003cstrong\u003eGiovanni De Franceso\u003c/strong\u003e; Sculptural totem by \u003cstrong\u003eNicholas Shurey\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/23_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/23_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1708\" alt=\"The elevator lobby at The Apartment, a guests-only lounge.\nPhotography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"The elevator lobby at The Apartment, a guests-only lounge.\nPhotography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/23_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eThe elevator lobby at \u003cstrong\u003eThe Apartment\u003c/strong\u003e, a guests-only lounge.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/24_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/24_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1716\" alt=\"Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/24_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n  \u003cp\u003eAt the heart of the hotel’s intimate ambiance is \u003cem\u003eThe Apartment\u003c/em\u003e, an exclusive lounge that feels like a mid-century collector’s dream come to life. \u003cstrong\u003eAscend the striking marble staircase, and you’re welcomed into a Gio Ponti-inspired setting where modernist design meets artisanal craftsmanship where Pompeian red walls, floor-to-ceiling bronze-framed mirrors and a mahoganized plywood divider set the tone.\u003c/strong\u003e Anchoring the space is a sculptural fireplace with a faceted metallic hood, flanked by two striking columns clad in handcrafted ceramic tiles by Los Angeles-based artist \u003ca href=\"https://www.benmedansky.com/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBen Medansky\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e. The ceramic bubble-like wall tiling, that is carried on from the elevator lobby, nods firmly to Ponti’s \u003cem\u003eParco dei Principi \u003c/em\u003ehotel in Sorrento. Every detail has been meticulously considered, from the bronze sconces and smoked-glass chandeliers (both custom-designed by Peer) to the complimentary cocktail cabinet and pantry that invite guests to indulge at their leisure.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/35_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_theapartment_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/35_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_theapartment_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1902\" alt=\"The Apartment, a guests-only lounge.\nCeramic columns by Ben Medansky.\nPhotography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"The Apartment, a guests-only lounge.\nCeramic columns by Ben Medansky.\nPhotography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/35_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_theapartment_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Apartment\u003c/strong\u003e, a guests-only lounge.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCeramic columns by Ben Medansky.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/36_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_theapartment_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/36_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_theapartment_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1911\" alt=\"The Apartment, a guests-only lounge.\nPhotography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"The Apartment, a guests-only lounge.\nPhotography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/36_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_theapartment_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Apartment\u003c/strong\u003e, a guests-only lounge.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/02_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/02_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1706\" alt=\"Superior King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"Superior King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/02_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eSuperior King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1911\" alt=\"King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eKing Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" alt=\"King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eKing Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/12_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/12_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1918\" alt=\"King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/12_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eKing Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003ePeer’s mastery of design shines through in The Manner’s 97 guest rooms, which include 10 suites and a show-stopping duplex penthouse, with bespoke Italian furnishings, floor-to-ceiling mirrors that reflect the cityscape, and asymmetrical chandeliers that cast an ambient glow.\u003cstrong\u003e The palette—ochres, sand tones, and light blues—is softened by rich textures like dark wood veneers and navy lacquer. \u003c/strong\u003eIn an intentional nod to serenity, there are no modern distractions such as televisions, allowing guests to immerse themselves in the carefully curated environment.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe pièce de résistance is of course the penthouse, a two-story haven perched on the 12th and 13th floors. Wrapped in shades of deep red, its sleek modernism channels Halston’s iconic Olympic Tower offices\u003c/strong\u003e—a paragon of minimalist excess, Halston’s sumptuous headquarters epitomized the luxurious, forward-thinking ethos of 1970s New York. A double-height window and mirror amplify the drama, bathing the space in light and showcasing sweeping views of Manhattan. The upstairs bedroom, complete with a travertine fireplace, leads to a private wraparound terrace where the skyline serves as the perfect backdrop for any occasion—be it a sunlit morning coffee or an intimate evening gathering.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1918\" alt=\"Superior Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"Superior Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eSuperior Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/05_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/05_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1705\" alt=\"Deluxe Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"Deluxe Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/05_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eDeluxe Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/06_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/06_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1918\" alt=\"Deluxe Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" title=\"Deluxe Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/06_the_manner_hotel_hannes_peer_architecture_chris_mottalini_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003eDeluxe Corner King Room. Photography by Chris Mottalini.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003